WEBVTT

00:07.640 --> 00:08.960
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:37.400 --> 01:42.960
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

01:52.080 --> 01:55.880
Yanlai, you had a formidable presence
at today's court.

01:59.000 --> 02:02.000
I personally decided to kill
the Northern Desert King.

02:03.040 --> 02:05.120
But clearly, you won't regret it.

02:05.200 --> 02:06.400
Since childhood,

02:06.920 --> 02:09.160
have I ever said "regret"?

02:09.240 --> 02:11.000
You've made up your mind.

02:12.200 --> 02:13.120
I won't stop you.

02:14.800 --> 02:15.920
You can't stop me.

02:16.560 --> 02:17.960
Before you go,

02:19.120 --> 02:20.680
let's do something first.

02:22.480 --> 02:25.920
Your mother's tablet
can be placed in our ancestral hall.

02:30.480 --> 02:31.520
What did you say?

02:33.520 --> 02:34.520
Yanlai,

02:36.320 --> 02:39.240
don't you always want her tablet
to be placed there?

02:39.840 --> 02:41.160
Now is the perfect time.

02:42.240 --> 02:45.520
You'll enter the pedigree too.
You and your mother

02:46.320 --> 02:48.760
will become rightful members
of the Xie family.

02:59.080 --> 03:00.000
No need.

03:05.440 --> 03:07.920
Rightful identity…

03:09.760 --> 03:11.280
Recognition of the clan…

03:11.360 --> 03:13.160
Don't you want any?

03:13.240 --> 03:15.040
I used to think

03:15.120 --> 03:17.760
it was all I sought, but now…

03:18.880 --> 03:20.000
Now what?

03:21.040 --> 03:23.520
My mother doesn't need
offerings of the Xie Family,

03:24.160 --> 03:27.440
and I don't need the recognition
from the Xie's pedigree.

03:28.360 --> 03:30.360
Nor do I need a rightful identity.

03:31.560 --> 03:33.160
I know who I am,

03:34.000 --> 03:35.720
and I know what I want.

03:36.800 --> 03:37.720
That's enough.

03:38.800 --> 03:40.800
After going through all this,

03:41.640 --> 03:43.840
you've really changed.

03:45.720 --> 03:47.320
Since you've made up your mind,

03:49.840 --> 03:50.720
so be it.

03:53.080 --> 03:54.040
Xie Yanfang.

03:57.040 --> 03:58.280
Five years ago,

03:59.320 --> 04:01.320
you gave me the Bloodburn Pill.

04:02.840 --> 04:04.240
Did you know

04:04.840 --> 04:06.120
anyone who took it

04:08.480 --> 04:09.560
would die?

04:18.519 --> 04:21.320
This secret elixir
only belongs to our direct line.

04:22.400 --> 04:23.920
It can even revive the dying.

04:24.520 --> 04:27.720
Keep it with you in case of emergency.

04:54.320 --> 04:55.200
Yanlai.

05:02.840 --> 05:04.240
How did you know I'm here?

05:05.000 --> 05:06.120
You're my brother.

05:06.880 --> 05:08.440
Of course, I keep track of where you go.

05:09.520 --> 05:10.560
I came here

05:11.160 --> 05:12.800
to take you back home.

05:15.720 --> 05:16.640
No need.

05:17.240 --> 05:20.640
Here in Yunzhong,
people go through wind and sand.

05:21.720 --> 05:23.800
Living by one's ability isn't too bad.

05:24.400 --> 05:26.000
Young Master cares for you.

05:26.080 --> 05:27.280
How could you be ungrateful?

05:27.360 --> 05:29.600
You really think Chu Ling trusts you?

05:29.680 --> 05:32.160
If he knows you're a Xie,
can you still stay?

05:32.240 --> 05:33.320
He wouldn't care.

05:34.600 --> 05:37.760
All he cares about
is whether I can slay enemies

05:38.480 --> 05:40.080
and guard this place.

05:40.680 --> 05:43.160
He doesn't care who I really am.

05:43.880 --> 05:45.760
Chu Ling has 200,000 frontier troops.

05:46.360 --> 05:47.480
If he wants to kill you,

05:48.120 --> 05:50.000
you won't be able to resist.

05:50.800 --> 05:51.840
Will you gamble?

05:53.240 --> 05:54.640
I have nothing to lose.

05:55.760 --> 05:56.960
I don't care.

05:57.840 --> 05:59.520
So, this is your choice.

06:18.040 --> 06:19.480
If I say I didn't know,

06:21.360 --> 06:22.240
will you believe me?

06:53.760 --> 06:56.120
Xie Yanlai didn't tell
his brother in advance.

06:56.200 --> 06:57.800
Xie Yanfang must be angry.

06:58.320 --> 06:59.320
Wrong.

06:59.920 --> 07:03.440
Xie Yanfang doesn't care
whether he was informed in advance.

07:04.120 --> 07:06.120
He has raised too many lackeys.

07:06.200 --> 07:07.680
It's normal that one of them

07:08.360 --> 07:09.520
may betray him.

07:10.640 --> 07:11.800
What matters to him?

07:14.560 --> 07:18.160
Xie Yanlai has won successive exploits
and enjoys supreme prestige.

07:18.800 --> 07:19.920
If it goes on like this,

07:20.840 --> 07:24.640
his reputation will overshadow
Xie Yanfang's.

07:25.240 --> 07:29.040
That's exactly what Xie Yanfang
won't allow to happen.

07:29.840 --> 07:30.680
It seems

07:31.680 --> 07:33.200
big changes are coming to his family.

07:33.280 --> 07:35.840
Don't underestimate Xie Yanfang.

07:36.640 --> 07:38.400
With his mastery of strategies,

07:38.480 --> 07:40.920
how would he not have a backup plan?

07:41.600 --> 07:44.040
There must still be room for a reversal.

07:44.840 --> 07:46.720
Let's not worry about them.

07:47.640 --> 07:49.720
Is everything ready for tonight's banquet?

07:50.480 --> 07:53.240
Rest assured. Everything is ready.

07:58.000 --> 08:02.920
TOMB OF THE LATE LADY XIE

08:13.000 --> 08:15.920
HER NAME WAS CUIYU.
A LIFE MARKED BY MISFORTUNE

08:23.760 --> 08:25.480
We agreed on a hundred liang of gold.

08:25.560 --> 08:26.800
Why is it 50 now?

08:26.880 --> 08:29.160
If the boy weren't a Xie,

08:29.240 --> 08:31.080
I wouldn't have risked my life for him.

08:31.160 --> 08:35.600
You got 50 liang of gold
for one single night.

08:35.679 --> 08:38.280
In my opinion, it's a good deal for you.

08:38.880 --> 08:41.640
That boy is the Xie's bloodline,

08:42.240 --> 08:45.000
but after all, he's an illegitimate child.

08:45.080 --> 08:47.240
Don't think he's very valuable.

08:48.120 --> 08:50.560
Send him back home as soon as you can.

08:50.640 --> 08:52.880
Don't delay my business tonight.

08:52.960 --> 08:54.240
Mother.

08:57.600 --> 09:01.920
Son, you've grown up.
You should be sensible.

09:02.000 --> 09:04.440
The Xie Family is where you belong.

09:04.520 --> 09:07.520
From now on, you'll enjoy a great life,
and that's enough.

09:08.880 --> 09:10.640
Come on, you…

09:15.000 --> 09:17.040
Listen. Mother isn't leaving.

09:17.120 --> 09:18.480
Let go, will you?

09:18.560 --> 09:21.280
I'll go buy some fabrics
to make you new clothes.

09:21.360 --> 09:23.720
I really won't leave.
Look. It's getting late.

09:23.800 --> 09:25.600
The cloth shop will be closed.

09:26.320 --> 09:27.480
Good boy.

09:27.560 --> 09:28.680
Come on.

09:32.080 --> 09:34.600
-Is he the ninth young master?
-That's right.

09:34.680 --> 09:37.280
Look. You're the young master now.
How can you wear ragged clothes?

09:37.360 --> 09:40.240
I'll go make you some new clothes.
Wait here.

09:44.640 --> 09:45.480
What is his name?

09:46.280 --> 09:48.480
Whatever. Call him anything you want.

10:01.280 --> 10:03.400
Mother, it's been long.

10:05.160 --> 10:06.280
When I was little,

10:08.440 --> 10:10.080
I thought you left for new clothes.

10:11.920 --> 10:14.240
So, I waited for you on the stairs
of Xie Residence.

10:15.320 --> 10:16.640
I waited until night.

10:18.920 --> 10:20.760
Until my candied hawthorn melted.

10:24.480 --> 10:25.640
But I still failed

10:28.000 --> 10:29.480
to see you back.

10:31.760 --> 10:32.760
Later,

10:33.280 --> 10:35.200
they said you were a dirty woman,

10:38.720 --> 10:40.080
and I was a courtesan's son.

10:41.320 --> 10:42.680
I studied really hard

10:43.600 --> 10:44.920
and learned martial arts.

10:46.120 --> 10:47.600
No matter how hard it was,

10:48.680 --> 10:50.040
it never felt bitter.

10:51.080 --> 10:52.320
I just wished

10:53.800 --> 10:55.360
that one day

10:56.800 --> 10:59.520
I could be a rightful member
of the Xie Family.

11:03.320 --> 11:05.360
I wanted them to think highly of me.

11:07.000 --> 11:08.560
I also hoped

11:11.560 --> 11:15.440
that your tablet could be placed
in their ancestral hall.

11:16.880 --> 11:21.160
To make this happen,
I endured insults and risked my life.

11:22.080 --> 11:24.040
Even if I felt like a ghost there,

11:27.840 --> 11:31.840
I felt happier than being
a wandering man as Fu Jiu.

11:31.920 --> 11:34.840
I used to think if I became successful,

11:34.920 --> 11:36.600
they wouldn't scorn us anymore.

11:36.680 --> 11:38.960
It turns out you abandoned me long ago.

11:39.040 --> 11:40.280
Right?

11:42.400 --> 11:43.760
I've never hated you.

11:45.400 --> 11:46.720
Even now,

11:48.480 --> 11:50.240
I still don't hate you.

11:52.400 --> 11:54.040
You suffered pains when bearing me.

11:55.120 --> 11:56.720
You pulled through when raising me.

11:58.160 --> 11:59.280
Maybe

12:01.320 --> 12:03.320
on the day you left me,

12:07.160 --> 12:08.920
you cried hard too.

12:11.360 --> 12:12.560
Right?

12:12.640 --> 12:13.920
I've figured out one thing.

12:14.600 --> 12:17.360
We can't get everything,
even if we fight for it.

12:17.440 --> 12:20.720
Mother, I met someone.

12:24.920 --> 12:26.920
The most important person in my life.

12:30.560 --> 12:32.000
Her name is Zhao.

12:33.560 --> 12:35.200
She made me understand

12:37.360 --> 12:39.360
a rightful identity doesn't matter.

12:41.040 --> 12:42.240
I am who I am.

12:44.720 --> 12:46.240
And I am your son.

12:51.800 --> 12:52.640
Jiu.

12:56.520 --> 12:57.800
Don't be sad.

13:09.840 --> 13:11.280
It's strange.

13:11.880 --> 13:15.440
Before, as Xie Yanlai, you would disdain

13:16.320 --> 13:18.320
and reject such useless comfort.

13:20.400 --> 13:22.040
But now, as Fu Jiu,

13:23.120 --> 13:25.120
you must want to hear this,

13:32.080 --> 13:33.080
"Don't be sad."

13:48.200 --> 13:49.360
I didn't expect this

13:53.520 --> 13:54.880
because I dared not.

13:57.960 --> 13:58.920
Nor could I get any.

14:01.720 --> 14:03.160
The rightful identity

14:06.320 --> 14:07.600
and the family love

14:10.080 --> 14:11.320
were out of my reach.

14:16.840 --> 14:18.920
So, I had to pretend I didn't want any.

14:22.200 --> 14:23.840
Only in this way could I relieve

14:24.720 --> 14:25.800
the pain and shame

14:28.240 --> 14:29.440
in my heart.

14:32.200 --> 14:33.040
But now,

14:34.760 --> 14:35.960
no need for that.

14:46.920 --> 14:49.360
Yeah. No need for that.

14:49.880 --> 14:51.680
Now I know who I am.

14:54.000 --> 14:55.360
Whether Xie Yanlai

14:55.880 --> 14:59.000
or Fu Jiu, I'm just myself.

15:00.640 --> 15:02.040
You're mine.

15:03.040 --> 15:04.720
In life,

15:05.720 --> 15:07.440
having the freedom to choose

15:08.400 --> 15:10.000
is already the greatest happiness.

15:12.280 --> 15:13.880
You're good as you are.

15:15.280 --> 15:18.440
But now, you're always hindered.

15:19.440 --> 15:22.560
If I kill the King,
the problem will be solved.

15:23.600 --> 15:25.080
That's my problem.

15:28.320 --> 15:31.640
Why didn't you tell me
before you made that decision?

15:32.240 --> 15:33.480
No need.

15:35.320 --> 15:36.560
You wouldn't let me go.

15:37.160 --> 15:39.680
My father and the King
fought for over a decade.

15:39.760 --> 15:41.160
Do you know how hard--?

15:41.720 --> 15:43.480
Zhao, I know.

15:44.080 --> 15:45.040
You worry about me.

15:46.360 --> 15:49.200
But this time,
let me do something for you.

16:11.880 --> 16:13.000
According to Father,

16:13.880 --> 16:17.600
the armor is a soldier's second life.

16:20.320 --> 16:22.200
You never wore it before

16:22.840 --> 16:26.080
because you thought your life
wasn't worth it.

16:28.320 --> 16:29.840
Now,

16:31.560 --> 16:32.760
I want you to put it on.

16:34.520 --> 16:35.400
I want you to know

16:36.560 --> 16:38.360
I'm waiting for you to return alive.

16:40.080 --> 16:41.800
Just like how my father

16:42.760 --> 16:44.600
took you out of the desert alive.

16:55.600 --> 16:56.440
All right.

16:59.400 --> 17:00.560
You make a vow.

17:04.440 --> 17:05.280
Make it to my father.

17:27.000 --> 17:28.280
I give you my word.

17:29.960 --> 17:31.720
I will come back alive.

17:39.960 --> 17:40.880
You must not lie to me.

17:46.240 --> 17:48.280
I swear to General Chu's armor.

17:51.200 --> 17:52.560
I will stay alive

17:54.000 --> 17:55.600
and return the armor to him.

18:26.240 --> 18:28.800
Xie Yanlai has become
even more uncontrollable.

18:28.880 --> 18:31.280
At today's court, he made a military vow

18:31.360 --> 18:32.920
to kill the Northern Desert King.

18:33.000 --> 18:34.920
Ministers were stunned.

18:37.200 --> 18:39.040
He's never a caged bird.

18:40.560 --> 18:41.600
Now that he's strong enough,

18:43.560 --> 18:45.320
he will surely leave.

18:47.640 --> 18:50.760
That man… He's back, huh?

18:50.840 --> 18:52.600
Yes, in the city.

18:52.680 --> 18:54.880
I heard he had great prestige

18:55.480 --> 18:56.560
among frontier troops.

18:57.320 --> 18:58.720
Glad to hear that.

19:00.440 --> 19:03.000
I think it's time to have the next general

19:04.040 --> 19:04.960
take the stage.

19:11.040 --> 19:16.360
GRACE OF THE LIANG GENERATIONS

19:21.760 --> 19:22.960
Mr. Liang is back.

19:24.080 --> 19:25.920
He's back.

19:26.000 --> 19:26.840
Come on.

19:27.920 --> 19:30.160
-He's back!
-Mr. Liang, you're finally back.

19:30.240 --> 19:33.160
-Not Mr. Liang. Now, he's General Liang.
-Mr. Liang!

19:33.240 --> 19:35.920
The Roving General titled by His Majesty.

19:37.800 --> 19:41.360
-And you are?
-General Liang, I'm Huang.

19:41.440 --> 19:44.200
General, why didn't you tell us before?

19:44.280 --> 19:46.040
We could have welcomed you from afar.

19:46.120 --> 19:47.880
-Yeah.
-That's right.

19:47.960 --> 19:50.280
You're the hero of our clan.

19:50.360 --> 19:51.800
Don't stand here. Let's get in.

19:51.880 --> 19:53.320
Yeah. Come in, please.

19:53.400 --> 19:54.760
-Get in.
-Come on.

19:54.840 --> 19:56.720
-This way.
-Hurry.

20:01.120 --> 20:04.480
NO UNAUTHORIZED ENTRY
SEVERE PUNISHMENT FOR VIOLATORS

20:07.400 --> 20:10.080
Father. Mother.

20:12.280 --> 20:14.480
I've only been a general for half a day,

20:16.080 --> 20:18.920
but visitors have already flooded in.

20:20.120 --> 20:21.680
Many relatives and friends

20:22.520 --> 20:24.600
were popping up.

20:28.720 --> 20:30.640
They greeted me warmly

20:32.200 --> 20:33.640
and shed tears

20:35.360 --> 20:36.960
for seeing me again.

20:37.480 --> 20:38.360
TABLET OF MR. LIANG

20:38.440 --> 20:40.960
Actually, I barely remember them.

20:43.040 --> 20:44.160
It doesn't matter.

20:44.760 --> 20:46.200
TABLET OF MRS. LIANG

20:50.240 --> 20:53.160
ANCESTRAL HALL OF THE LIANG FAMILY

20:57.640 --> 21:01.320
Soon, everyone in the Capital will know

21:01.920 --> 21:03.080
I can bring glory

21:04.000 --> 21:06.320
to the Liang Family.

21:49.680 --> 21:51.960
The honey filling is overflowing.

21:52.040 --> 21:53.240
Way too sweet.

21:53.320 --> 21:55.080
Is it for Commander Xie?

21:55.160 --> 21:57.360
Oh no. It's for General Fu Jiu, right?

21:58.920 --> 22:00.760
His journey is really concerning.

22:02.080 --> 22:04.400
-Shall I divine for him?
-No need.

22:05.680 --> 22:07.320
He never believes in fate.

22:11.320 --> 22:12.360
Letter from the Stronghold.

22:12.440 --> 22:14.440
They found the old file
of Xiaonan caravan.

22:27.280 --> 22:30.120
As expected, three months before the fire,

22:30.200 --> 22:31.880
they passed the village six times.

22:33.280 --> 22:35.440
Why did you suddenly investigate
such an old case?

22:36.120 --> 22:39.560
Jiu figured out
the fire resulted from fire oil.

22:40.160 --> 22:43.360
It might be transported
for the Northern Desert.

22:45.360 --> 22:46.560
Judging from the file,

22:47.240 --> 22:49.960
this caravan passed six times.

22:50.040 --> 22:52.320
But every time,
they carried very few goods.

22:52.400 --> 22:56.280
That wasn't something
a normal caravan would do.

22:57.080 --> 22:58.200
It had to be something else.

22:59.120 --> 23:00.760
What could it be?

23:00.840 --> 23:03.040
Wei Village only had dozens of villagers

23:03.120 --> 23:04.520
and uninhabited wilderness.

23:05.200 --> 23:06.720
What could they be up to?

23:08.480 --> 23:10.080
So, Jiu was right.

23:11.600 --> 23:13.040
Northern Desert foes
conspired with Xiaonan

23:13.120 --> 23:14.480
to burn the Wei Village

23:15.280 --> 23:17.160
with an aim at Cangmu Stronghold.

23:19.240 --> 23:21.440
To be exact, my mother.

23:23.960 --> 23:26.240
To reveal my mother was an enemy general

23:27.280 --> 23:29.440
would be the best weapon
against my father.

23:30.240 --> 23:34.320
In that case, frontier troops
would have a new master.

23:36.400 --> 23:41.960
That would benefit Xiaonan
and the Northern Desert.

23:43.640 --> 23:46.200
Xiao Xun and his father
even struck a deal with evil enemies.

23:46.800 --> 23:48.520
Then we'll let them know

23:49.920 --> 23:52.720
how it feels to be devoured
by their own ambition.

24:17.760 --> 24:19.160
Why are we meeting here?

24:21.040 --> 24:22.400
Because your girl

24:23.360 --> 24:25.240
has a lot to say to you.

24:26.200 --> 24:27.920
But a princess can't say that.

24:31.320 --> 24:32.160
More maltose was used.

24:33.920 --> 24:35.200
It's sweeter.

24:36.000 --> 24:36.840
You made it?

24:42.360 --> 24:43.600
It feels sweet enough just looking at it.

24:45.400 --> 24:48.120
Jiu, you've picked up sweet talk.

24:51.200 --> 24:52.480
I can do more

24:53.560 --> 24:54.960
than you think I can.

24:58.240 --> 25:01.360
You must eat it. I made it overnight.

25:05.760 --> 25:09.480
I've never seen you in armor before.
What a young general.

25:10.440 --> 25:11.600
You look so gallant.

25:12.640 --> 25:14.120
No wonder the ladies in Yunzhong

25:15.360 --> 25:17.080
compliment your looks.

25:25.560 --> 25:27.160
Their compliments

25:28.560 --> 25:30.040
aren't as sweet as yours.

25:31.840 --> 25:32.960
And they aren't

25:35.640 --> 25:36.920
as pretty as you.

25:47.840 --> 25:48.800
Don't forget

25:49.880 --> 25:51.440
what you promised me.

25:59.920 --> 26:00.920
I won't.

26:04.920 --> 26:07.920
When I'm back, I'll return it.

26:10.000 --> 26:10.840
Return?

26:12.480 --> 26:13.640
Both.

26:15.440 --> 26:16.440
The armor and me.

26:17.280 --> 26:20.120
If you doubt it… Words are no proof.

26:23.520 --> 26:24.720
Let this be my pledge.

27:46.880 --> 27:50.320
<i>Zhao, you were meant</i>

27:51.560 --> 27:54.280
<i>to soar up there. And my role</i>

27:55.400 --> 27:57.000
<i>is to uphold you.</i>

27:58.080 --> 28:02.520
CAPITAL

28:16.400 --> 28:19.040
Tang, why did you come to me?

28:19.120 --> 28:22.880
Are you going to see your parents?

28:26.960 --> 28:27.800
Zhao,

28:28.640 --> 28:30.560
I used to think

28:30.640 --> 28:34.000
manipulating the court like you
would be truly great.

28:34.880 --> 28:37.160
And after going through various schemes,

28:37.240 --> 28:41.040
I realized to be a hero
was the real thrill.

28:41.760 --> 28:45.640
However, it might not be right for me.

28:50.720 --> 28:53.800
Since I was little, I've dreamed
of having a good husband

28:54.400 --> 28:55.720
and living a life

28:55.800 --> 28:58.160
inside my house as a good wife and mother.

28:59.720 --> 29:01.920
But now, I've changed my mind.

29:02.640 --> 29:03.600
It's because of you.

29:04.800 --> 29:05.760
You've taught me.

29:05.840 --> 29:10.520
Even if we're women,
we can still do a lot.

29:13.040 --> 29:15.880
Even though I can't become an official,

29:16.680 --> 29:19.800
the world is big enough,
and I can go out to experience it.

29:27.880 --> 29:28.720
Here.

29:32.960 --> 29:36.480
Recent literary gatherings
make me understand.

29:37.080 --> 29:41.080
Giving chances to ladies like me
for them to shine

29:42.320 --> 29:44.920
makes me even happier than my own glory.

29:46.280 --> 29:50.520
So, I intend to introduce
literary gatherings elsewhere

29:50.600 --> 29:52.480
to enlighten more ladies.

29:53.080 --> 29:56.720
They don't need to live
within others' expectations.

29:57.640 --> 30:01.480
They deserve the world of their own.

30:07.120 --> 30:08.040
Then this world

30:09.600 --> 30:11.040
will shine because of you.

30:21.080 --> 30:23.680
Did you just let Xie Yanlai go?

30:25.560 --> 30:26.960
Don't be silly.

30:28.320 --> 30:31.960
A lot of people in the court
want Xie Yanlai dead.

30:32.560 --> 30:34.400
I don't have to do anything.

30:35.840 --> 30:36.680
‎Really?

30:37.600 --> 30:40.080
-For example?
-Don't you remember?

30:41.880 --> 30:44.640
The famous gentleman of the Xie Family.

30:44.720 --> 30:47.480
Do you mean Xie Yanfang?

30:48.080 --> 30:50.640
It can't be that easy to kill
the Northern Desert King.

30:50.720 --> 30:53.280
Chu Ling couldn't do that
within 20 years on the frontier.

30:53.840 --> 30:55.200
How can Xie Yanlai do it?

30:55.280 --> 30:58.840
What if Xie Yanlai really succeeds?

31:00.680 --> 31:02.680
Then he can't live.

31:04.720 --> 31:07.000
A lackey who only takes orders

31:07.600 --> 31:09.920
betrayed his master twice in a row.

31:10.800 --> 31:12.640
Xie Yanfang won't let him live.

31:13.760 --> 31:15.360
In the Xie Family,

31:16.240 --> 31:18.280
Xie Yanlai has been abandoned.

31:48.840 --> 31:49.880
Why again?

31:51.040 --> 31:52.160
I wanted to divine for General.

31:52.760 --> 31:56.680
But Her Highness told me
he didn't believe in this.

31:56.760 --> 31:58.880
-Then don't do that.
-But…

32:00.960 --> 32:04.160
What lies ahead is dangerous.
And Her Highness made a vow.

32:04.760 --> 32:08.600
When she's the Grand Princess,
she won't marry or have children.

32:08.680 --> 32:12.000
Then, her power won't fall to anyone
or benefit anyone.

32:12.080 --> 32:13.480
If she breaks her vow…

32:14.640 --> 32:17.560
What if Her Highness falls for him
and her vow comes true?

32:17.640 --> 32:19.480
Then don't divine.

32:20.720 --> 32:22.600
Who says a princess can't love?

32:23.400 --> 32:24.480
It makes sense.

32:25.320 --> 32:28.680
As the saying goes,
love is bound by destiny.

32:28.760 --> 32:31.400
In love, no one can be forced.

32:31.480 --> 32:33.120
Nor can anyone

32:33.920 --> 32:35.320
run away from it.

32:37.760 --> 32:40.880
But the state matters. So do the people.

32:41.840 --> 32:45.400
They weigh more than romance.

32:45.480 --> 32:49.280
But if you have to cage your heart, what…

32:49.360 --> 32:51.320
What's the difference from being a puppet?

32:56.920 --> 32:58.080
Difference?

32:58.920 --> 33:01.640
The difference is, a puppet has no choice.

33:02.240 --> 33:05.800
But I have the power to choose.

33:07.480 --> 33:11.160
He went to war for me.
Then I'll guard the court.

33:12.840 --> 33:15.320
I will protect the state.

33:16.320 --> 33:18.360
And I'll make it impregnable.

33:19.360 --> 33:21.480
Then the one I love can be safe.

33:23.240 --> 33:26.800
This is my choice.

33:32.720 --> 33:35.760
After the siege, Wangcheng

33:35.840 --> 33:38.080
was in ruins, awaiting revival.

33:38.160 --> 33:40.160
The court took it seriously

33:40.240 --> 33:43.120
and opened up Wangcheng trade route.

33:43.200 --> 33:44.800
In that case, we need

33:45.480 --> 33:48.480
a supervisor of the Maritime Trade Office
for commercial affairs.

33:49.080 --> 33:52.440
This supervisor must excel
in frontier trade.

33:52.520 --> 33:53.920
Mr. Xie, since we have candidates,

33:54.760 --> 33:56.280
why don't we recommend them

33:57.200 --> 33:59.040
for His Majesty to choose from?

33:59.840 --> 34:02.520
I recommend Zhao Su,
pupil of the Xie Family.

34:02.600 --> 34:05.040
He knows trade routes very well.

34:05.120 --> 34:07.360
I recommend Zhou Ming, pupil of Mr. Deng.

34:07.440 --> 34:09.239
He was in charge of water transport.

34:09.840 --> 34:11.440
This is a serious matter.

34:11.520 --> 34:14.360
We request Your Majesty
and Your Highness to make the decision.

34:15.320 --> 34:18.000
Mr. Deng and Mr. Xie
are important ministers.

34:18.080 --> 34:19.880
Their pupils have unique talents.

34:20.400 --> 34:21.880
How about they take charge together?

34:23.080 --> 34:26.320
Zhou Ming, Mr. Deng's pupil,
excels in finance.

34:26.400 --> 34:29.880
Zhao Su, Mr. Xie's pupil,
knows frontier trade.

34:30.480 --> 34:32.840
Balancing each other,
they're a perfect match.

34:33.800 --> 34:34.840
I approve.

34:34.920 --> 34:36.639
Hereby, Zhou Ming and Zhao Su

34:36.719 --> 34:39.080
take charge of frontier trade taxes

34:39.159 --> 34:40.960
and customs clearance.

34:42.280 --> 34:44.239
Let me add one more thing.

34:44.960 --> 34:47.800
Wangcheng trade route
concerns frontier defense.

34:48.480 --> 34:51.159
I propose that special goods

34:51.239 --> 34:54.000
can't be transported without my approval.

34:54.639 --> 34:57.640
What are the special goods
Your Highness is talking about?

34:58.800 --> 34:59.640
Fire oil.

35:11.680 --> 35:13.720
FERRYMAN’S LODGE

35:13.800 --> 35:18.040
Your Highness, Chu Zhao
got our old ledgers by some means.

35:18.800 --> 35:20.000
At today's court, she proposed

35:20.080 --> 35:22.800
transport of fire oil
should need her approval.

35:23.520 --> 35:25.760
How on earth did she learn of this?

35:26.800 --> 35:28.320
Didn't I tell you?

35:28.400 --> 35:31.320
Nothing shall go wrong with the ledgers!

35:31.400 --> 35:34.920
Your Highness, Chu Zhao sent men
to watch us closely.

35:35.000 --> 35:36.000
We really can't guard against her.

35:37.560 --> 35:39.200
She made one move after another

35:40.120 --> 35:42.080
just to make me panic.

35:42.840 --> 35:45.760
We'll set this aside for now.

35:46.440 --> 35:47.400
You…

35:47.480 --> 35:49.320
Send men to monitor Mr. Deng's mansion.

35:49.960 --> 35:52.040
Anything suspicious will be reported!

35:53.320 --> 35:54.520
Deng Yi

35:55.560 --> 35:57.560
is our last card.

35:58.280 --> 36:00.120
Nothing shall go wrong with him!

36:00.920 --> 36:02.040
I'm on it.

36:07.280 --> 36:11.440
IMPERIAL GUARD OFFICE

36:11.520 --> 36:13.360
Her Highness titled Mu Xiaoman

36:13.440 --> 36:15.760
Commander of the Imperial Guard Office?

36:18.280 --> 36:20.640
At today's court, you mentioned fire oil.

36:20.720 --> 36:23.360
I guess Xiao Xun will soon
lose his composure.

36:25.080 --> 36:27.400
My goal is to make him panic.

36:28.040 --> 36:29.240
Look.

36:29.320 --> 36:33.320
Only six hours later,
he sent his men to Mr. Deng's mansion.

36:34.840 --> 36:36.200
He wants Deng Yi to help?

36:36.840 --> 36:39.840
Deng Yi is in deep trouble himself,
crushed by Xie Yanfang.

36:41.480 --> 36:43.560
So, Mr. Deng is looking for a solution.

36:44.160 --> 36:47.800
The 25 guests for his banquet
are powerful officers,

36:47.880 --> 36:50.800
like commandants, captains,
and adjutant generals.

36:51.840 --> 36:54.240
He's a civil officer, but has a sharp eye.

36:55.080 --> 36:56.080
He's scared.

36:56.720 --> 36:59.000
Xie Yanfang holds military power.

36:59.080 --> 37:01.480
I command frontier troops.

37:01.560 --> 37:03.640
He needs to find some biting fighters

37:04.320 --> 37:07.200
to prevent himself from being eliminated.

37:07.880 --> 37:09.520
These are their attendants,

37:09.600 --> 37:12.160
including personal servants,
guards, and carters.

37:12.240 --> 37:13.520
Seventy-two in total.

37:14.560 --> 37:17.800
Oh. The new Roving General Liang Qiang

37:17.880 --> 37:20.160
was also invited to that banquet.

37:20.240 --> 37:22.040
When he was at the frontier,

37:22.120 --> 37:23.920
he had an unusual promotion.

37:24.720 --> 37:27.080
At that time, I guessed
he had some backing.

37:27.680 --> 37:29.160
So, it's Mr. Deng.

37:30.560 --> 37:31.920
Wise choice.

37:32.480 --> 37:34.880
Why did Deng Yi choose Liang Qiang?

37:35.880 --> 37:38.360
Back then, he was merely
a soldier at Wangcheng.

37:38.440 --> 37:41.200
-He had no power.
-Just because he was a mere soldier,

37:41.280 --> 37:44.040
he was more eager
to get promoted by any means.

37:44.960 --> 37:47.680
Besides, he wasn't a mere soldier.

37:50.360 --> 37:52.600
His clan was involved
with the Third Prince.

37:52.680 --> 37:54.200
That was a big clan.

37:54.280 --> 37:56.480
But they were exiled
for taking the wrong side.

37:57.440 --> 38:00.840
He turned from a rich young man
into a frontier soldier.

38:01.440 --> 38:04.120
How would he not resent it or hate it?

38:04.720 --> 38:06.280
Resentment and hatred

38:06.920 --> 38:09.040
-lead to ambitions.
-Exactly.

38:10.360 --> 38:11.720
Once a man like him

38:11.800 --> 38:14.600
gets a glimmer of hope,
he'll seize the chance

38:15.320 --> 38:17.960
and even work with the devil.

38:18.040 --> 38:20.960
So there's so much in court politics.

38:21.640 --> 38:23.080
I must learn carefully from Your Highness.

38:27.600 --> 38:29.760
Your Highness, have some tea I made.

38:39.320 --> 38:41.200
-Any more intel?
-The relationships

38:41.280 --> 38:43.680
in Mr. Deng's family
and his guests' family.

38:43.760 --> 38:46.480
Time was too short. It's not detailed.

38:52.360 --> 38:55.480
Four horses and five carriages.

38:55.560 --> 38:58.000
Even the number of trees is recorded.

38:58.080 --> 38:59.400
It's not detailed?

39:00.400 --> 39:03.280
Xiaoman, so besides fighting,

39:03.360 --> 39:05.640
you're also great at other things.

39:05.720 --> 39:07.720
I should learn from you.

39:08.240 --> 39:09.800
It's nothing.

39:09.880 --> 39:12.760
When I was at Cangmu Stronghold,
I scouted before taking action.

39:13.360 --> 39:15.480
The size of the family,
the location of the door and window,

39:15.560 --> 39:17.680
warehouses, and carriages…
All information was needed.

39:19.160 --> 39:20.960
I thought you couldn't handle this.

39:21.040 --> 39:22.360
I underestimated you.

39:22.960 --> 39:25.000
Most of the conversations
at Mr. Deng's banquet

39:25.080 --> 39:26.560
have been recorded.

39:27.200 --> 39:31.680
But we failed to eavesdrop
on confidential conversations.

39:32.520 --> 39:36.240
You just started doing this.
No hurry. Take your time.

39:36.320 --> 39:40.240
Now, you command 700 guards
of the Imperial Guard Office.

39:40.320 --> 39:42.080
You supervise on my orders.

39:42.160 --> 39:45.000
You act discreetly
just to avoid disturbing people

39:45.080 --> 39:46.680
and causing unnecessary trouble.

39:46.760 --> 39:49.880
But even if you're caught,
you don't need to flee.

39:50.840 --> 39:52.760
-I got it.
-Besides,

39:53.320 --> 39:54.560
I set up the Imperial Guard Office,

39:54.640 --> 39:57.680
so that you can openly command
some of the Longwei Army.

39:57.760 --> 40:00.040
Actually, there is a bigger purpose.

40:00.960 --> 40:03.760
Monitor every move of the frontier troops

40:03.840 --> 40:05.240
and report it to me immediately.

40:06.880 --> 40:09.600
You're doing this
for Xie Yanlai, aren't you?

40:10.280 --> 40:12.760
To clear the obstacles
from his killing mission.

40:15.960 --> 40:18.600
Don't blab. Leave. Leave now.

40:31.080 --> 40:34.440
Jiu, I hope this will help you.
